{"tid":2141612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得777政府擺明要你哋乖乖做生活得返工嘅港豬","createTime":"2020-08-05T23:32:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T06:33:05.000Z","uid":123613,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b175ac96d3206451b289bccbf2c6a6060e623358","tid":2141612,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:32:00.000Z","msg":"守咗咁耐 上個月大家仲開心咁迎接放寬限聚令之後嘅時光 唔洗一個月就爆第三波 而且爆得仲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府可以WFH但好多私人公司唔聽<br />\n全日禁堂食又無視市面仲有好多打工仔嘅事實<br />\n限聚令下好多可以玩嘅地方封晒<br />\n旅行唔駛諗 台灣日本見香港咁爆都未必想你哋過去<br />\n藍絲想返鄰國 鄰國仲即時封返轉頭<br />\n<br />\n有冇人覺得個777政府真係好成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功令到黃藍班人除返工之外 唔好諗去玩去旅行嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebe3b00f40eb86aa5bc3a86d4516589672db1bb","tid":2141612,"uid":16465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀 做運動都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慘過屋企隻狗"},{"pid":"19eeafcd414719d4698055b9f41de7d9e4aa545d","tid":2141612,"uid":123613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ebe3b00f40eb86aa5bc3a86d4516589672db1bb","tid":2141612,"uid":16465,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:34:31.000Z","msg":"啱呀 做運動都唔俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慘過屋企隻狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:36:43.000Z","msg":"跑步行山都要戴住口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c243a2784ab0caa6045eb1dccc3234abde689ed7","tid":2141612,"uid":218082,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T23:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCNOQEf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCNOQEf.jpg&h=a2c85367&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXi6Cjg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXi